      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          Do you offer home consultations?
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes! We offer complimentary home consultations for custom furniture projects. Contact us to schedule an appointment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          What is your delivery timeframe?
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Standard items are delivered within 2-4 weeks. Custom pieces typically take 6-8 weeks depending on complexity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          Do you ship nationwide?
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes, we ship across India. Delivery charges vary based on location and order size.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          What payment methods do you accept?
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We accept cash, credit/debit cards, bank transfers, and offer flexible EMI options for larger purchases.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
